IUFHji3w=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="d18474fd-7a40-49a6-90fd-368f7a68a903"><source>If this function is enabled, the system dynamically adjusts battery usage based on the electricity price curve and load prediction, and may temporarily not take action to reserve energy for higher-yield periods.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="4">If this function is enabled, the system dynamically adjusts battery usage based on the electricity price curve and load prediction, and may temporarily not take action to reserve energy for higher-yield periods.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="4">Als deze functie is ingeschakeld, past het systeem het batterijgebruik dynamisch aan op basis van de elektriciteitsprijscurve en belastingsvoorspelling, en kan het tijdelijk geen actie ondernemen om energie te reserveren voor periodes met een hogere opbrengst.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="4"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">VijtINlwvlzZ6f1tIhiqqd64Qec=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="888fb55f-28ae-4713-b774-ebcbe73798da"><source>Load demand met:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5">Load demand met:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5">Aan belastingsvraag voldaan:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="5"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">neMAixUcC7UflYfOm7GajF/jMcU=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="06531a34-8ecc-46ec-9a5f-2d705d14ed92"><source>If the PV power is just enough to meet the load demand, the system may prioritize the load, and there is no surplus power for charging the battery.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">If the PV power is just enough to meet the load demand, the system may prioritize the load, and there is no surplus power for charging the battery.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">Als het PV-vermogen net voldoende is om aan de belastingsvraag te voldoen, kan het systeem prioriteit geven aan de belasting en is er geen overtollig vermogen voor het opladen van de batterij.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="6"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">+C8sO09TaVsJ+FWJ/KmccHdPoqo=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="0518de6e-7c70-4f90-840c-b93d3d154cff"><source>SOC (energy) limit</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">SOC (energy) limit</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">SOC-limiet (energie)</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="7" locked="true"><sdl:rep id="S6ds+rDl2XBodazZVkH139iaEUE=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">S6ds+rDl2XBodazZVkH139iaEUE=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="03b257ce-60e8-40cb-87e4-b5d8c09e20f1"><source><g id="4">Backup power SOC protection mechanism</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8"><g id="4">Backup power SOC protection mechanism</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8"><g id="4">Beschermingsmechanisme back-upvermogen-SOC</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="8" locked="true"><sdl:rep id="FzX2NYWFQc+jvjyw9JetJw7ABys=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">FzX2NYWFQc+jvjyw9JetJw7ABys=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="273c4527-43c1-4f87-ad54-25cea3ff0016"><source>To ensure the power supply capability in the event of unexpected power outages, the system sets the peak shaving backup power SOC (for example, 20%) or off-grid backup power SOC (for example, 5%).</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">To ensure the power supply capability in the event of unexpected power outages, the system sets the peak shaving backup power SOC (for example, 20%) or off-grid backup power SOC (for example, 5%).</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">Om de stroomvoorziening bij onverwachte stroomuitval te waarborgen, stelt het systeem de SOC back-upvoeding voor piekbelastingafvlakking (bijvoorbeeld 20%) of de off-grid SOC back-upvoeding (bijvoorbeeld 5%) in.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="9"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">eABPihTL7v/8W6fE1KEo6SGWhqE=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="918b66aa-e881-46e5-a9ac-ab95a56099e4"><source>If the battery SOC is lower than this threshold at night, the system prevents the battery from discharging.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10">If the battery SOC is lower than this threshold at night, the system prevents the battery from discharging.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10">Als de batterij-SOC 's nachts lager is dan deze drempelwaarde, voorkomt het systeem dat de batterij ontlaadt.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="10" locked="true"><sdl:rep id="36Xxq1zuwcLHk+qVigBn2gypbpg=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">36Xxq1zuwcLHk+qVigBn2gypbpg=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="584d7251-42c9-4a4a-8fc1-e259ad5a05ae"><source><g id="7">End-of-discharge SOC</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11"><g id="7">End-of-discharge SOC</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11"><g id="7">Einde-ontlaad-SOC</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="11" locked="true"><sdl:rep id="hUZZq50gQbhGZ9jtni6CjIwXMo8=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">hUZZq50gQbhGZ9jtni6CjIwXMo8=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="56c469b5-d635-42fc-89b9-4f001dec55be"><source>If the battery SOC decreases to the end-of-discharge SOC (for example, 10%), the system forcibly stops discharging to prevent overdischarge.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12">If the battery SOC decreases to the end-of-discharge SOC (for example, 10%), the system forcibly stops discharging to prevent overdischarge.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12">Als de batterij-SOC daalt tot de einde-ontlaad-SOC (bijv. 10%), stopt het systeem geforceerd met ontladen om overontlading te voorkomen.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="12" locked="true"><sdl:rep id="Q7R9uJNJQqbjl5J2WC+5RWJPC9Y=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">Q7R9uJNJQqbjl5J2WC+5RWJPC9Y=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="25492e41-6250-4bff-a7f3-2b064cc5989a"><source>Operating mode and function configuration</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="13">Operating mode and function configuration</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="13">Bedrijfsmodus en functieconfiguratie</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="13"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">3yEXG48kD2cRx0ZtunpTRPFN5vk=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="fc9275ee-c16f-4da5-9641-da5af542f59e"><source><g id="11"><x id="9" /></g><g id="11"> </g><g id="11">time segment setting error</g>:</source><seg-source><g id="11"><x id="9" /></g><g id="11"> </g><mrk mtype="seg" mid="14"><g id="11">time segment setting error</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><g id="11"><x id="9" /></g><g id="11"> </g><mrk mtype="seg" mid="14"><g id="11">fout bij instellen van tijdsegment</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="14"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">ExOhKl94atQADJPXtMIU7CNNy4Q=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="384e58da-0481-4649-bb62-4ab410c785ff"><source>If the <x id="12" /> time segment does not cover the battery charge and discharge window, the system may not be able to trigger actions.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="15">If the <x id="12" /> time segment does not cover the battery charge and discharge window, the system may not be able to trigger actions.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="15">Als het tijdsegment <x id="12" /> het laad- en ontlaadvenster van de batterij niet dekt, kan het systeem mogelijk geen acties activeren.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="15"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">4UkhJKS4lddQN/9vIeFXX+kmuUQ=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="c42875de-9be6-44e2-aba5-9f74ccf0ffb8"><source><g id="16"><x id="14" /> disabled</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="16"><g id="16"><x id="14" /> disabled</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="16"><g id="16"><x id="14" /> uitgeschakeld</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="16" locked="true"><sdl:rep id="LC0vmNaTHyvyQVMYtHZDxIuUDcU=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">LC0vmNaTHyvyQVMYtHZDxIuUDcU=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="90348bff-68af-43f0-852e-35a6fb6c8084"><source>In <x id="17" /> mode, if <x id="18" /> is not manually enabled, the battery cannot be charged from the grid.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="17">In <x id="17" /> mode, if <x id="18" /> is not manually enabled, the battery cannot be charged from the grid.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="17">In de modus <x id="17" /> kan de batterij niet vanaf het net worden opgeladen als <x id="18" /> niet handmatig is ingeschakeld.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="17"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">tX2uj1ZTv9hNJkYkucqIvBAejpY=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="38b7ec0c-5617-4c63-8899-0fc1713054b7"><source>Consequently, the battery may be inoperable due to insufficient energy.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="18">Consequently, the battery may be inoperable due to insufficient energy.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="18">Als gevolg hiervan kan de batterij mogelijk niet werken vanwege onvoldoende energie.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="18"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">JAuN6g5Wur/Ihjh4o6QaGm7hc5I=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="69461da6-1a42-4e23-963e-ac2f3ff3b7e1"><source><g id="21">Mode conflict</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="19"><g id="21">Mode conflict</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="19"><g id="21">Modusconflict</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="19"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">l7Ki2bi7ZPxJ5gboOv11VmPN5yY=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="500f755b-d3e1-4528-ba1a-de0a050763e2"><source>If the <x id="22" /> mode is set, the battery can only be charged by PV power and cannot be charged from the grid.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="20">If the <x id="22" /> mode is set, the battery can only be charged by PV power and cannot be charged from the grid.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="20">Als de modus <x id="22" /> is ingesteld, kan de batterij alleen worden opgeladen met PV-vermogen en kan deze niet vanaf het net worden opgeladen.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="20"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">OV4pW0tVhQ8CIiOl1DM5FqFzDO0=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="ad5f8ad1-ce69-43c9-8d69-169cea5f1f72"><source>If PV power is insufficient, the battery cannot be charged.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="21">If PV power is insufficient, the battery cannot be charged.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="21">Als het PV-vermogen onvoldoende is, kan de batterij niet worden opgeladen.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="21"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">4sNNlQQp/ZRgcqsryDx2Sua4yJg=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group></body></file></xliff>